Logs the raw value of any assigned SMART attribute.
.RS 4
.PD 0
.HP 4
.I <id>
The SMART attribute ID (uint).
.HP 4
.I <raw_decimal>
The raw attribute value (uint, decimal).
.HP 4
.I <raw_hex>
The raw attribute value (uint, hexadecimal).
.HP 4
.I <norm>
The normalized value (uint).
.HP 4
.I <worst>
The worst value (uint).
.HP 4
.I <thresh>
The threshold value (uint).
.HP 4
.I <name>
Name of the attribute.
.HP 4
.I <type>
Type of the attribute: \`prefail\` or \`oldage\`.
.HP 4
.I <updated>
Update method of the attribute: \`always\` or \`offline\`.
